{"tid":539829,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北韓籲南北韓人民合力謀求統一 不需其他國家幫助","createTime":"2018-01-25T02:05:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-25T07:44:16.000Z","uid":39464,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"c00548a48995b74e8df0a96f8d76510bfae29748","tid":539829,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T02:05:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180125/large/1516836482_549f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180125%2Flarge%2F1516836482_549f.jpg&h=340a5c80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n北韓周四罕有地向「國內外所有韓國人」發出公告，表示他們應在沒有其他國家協助下，為統一作出突破。<br />\n<br />\n公告表示所有韓國人應「在南北韓之間促進聯繫、旅遊和合作」，平壤政府將「打垮」所有阻止朝鮮半島統一的圖謀。公告又說，韓國人應採取斷然行動，化解朝鮮半島的軍事緊張局面，創造和平環境。<br />\n<br />\n北韓官方朝中社說，朝鮮半島的軍事緊張，是改善韓國內部關係和統一的基本障礙，而與「外部力量」進行聯合軍演對發展南北韓關係沒有幫助。<br />\n<br />\n北韓在作出公告前，政府與政黨曾舉行聯合會議，支持領袖金正恩在元旦致辭中關於朝鮮半島統一的言論<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180125/57751107\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180125%2F57751107&d=lYIdUSeY49PtrXZ8XFOxu5zN29kXmk9bB7xBuKM86BA%3D&h=10502bb3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180125%2F57751107&h=6c761fc9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180125/57751107</a>"},{"pid":"ac62f34809e62dd1f35489912f6272d50b8a76be","tid":539829,"uid":35430,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T04:10:59.000Z","msg":"大中華毒<br />\n大韓民毒<br />\n大和民族"},{"pid":"0e072b13e882d381296e947934c586a857f4b0d7","tid":539829,"uid":41969,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T04:11:38.000Z","msg":"肥仔想上apink了"},{"pid":"c98d7147fe82041e43ca8418b149b64cc39ad768","tid":539829,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c